title: Hints - Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh Hello
description:
Meet Hints, a four piece of art school graduates that came together after being introduced by mutual friends. They have been playing together for a little over a year, and have since been fine-tuning their songwriting process and constantly working together to perfect their sound. Listen to the band talk about the value of studio quality and how it affects the dynamics of recording.
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
